'''Mr. IceBlock''' is a [[badguy]] in [[Icy Island]]. When jumped upon, ''Mr. IceBlock'' becomes a block of ice for a limited amount of time. This block of ice can be carried around by [[Tux]]. When released or when kicked, the block will glide away at a high speed, hurting everything in it's way. A gliding block of ice can be stopped by jumping on it.

